dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Riverside East / South 1/2 of San Bernardino South quadrangles, San Bernardino and Riverside County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Riverside East and South 1/2 San Bernardino South map
Geology Riverside and South 1/2 San Bernardino South quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base maps from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle RIVERSIDE EAST, CA 1967, AMS 2551 IV NE - V895, photorevised 1973; SAN BERNARDINO SOUTH, CA 1967 AMS 2552 III SE - Series V 895, photorevised 1973."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
